(56, 'Tai Chi Movements & Exercises : Tai Chi Ball Exerc', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DHN8fHZxBA8&feature=youtube_gdata', 3, '720', 'One of the benefits of tai chi balls is that they reinforce principles, such as breathing. Discover how tai chi balls can be used to set up resistance in movements with help from a tai chi instructor in this free video on tai chi ball exercises.\n\nExpert: Bob Waers\nContact: www.youhealthcenter.com/\nBio: Bob Waers trained directly with Grand Master Chan Pui of the Wah Lum kung fu system for 12 years.\nFilmmaker: Suzie Vigon', 'English', 52261, 'Tutorial', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/DHN8fHZxBA8/0.jpg', 'tai chi, exercise, demo, tutorial'),
(57, 'MASTERS OF HEAVEN & EARTH - Official Trailer by Em', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dwNXaQwjEr4', 3, '240', 'This is the trailer for Masters of Heaven and Earth. If you thought Tai Chi was old folks in the park moving slowly you will be shocked. Come with us on a journey across China to explore real Tai chi chuan. Featuring Chen style, Wudang tai chi and Yang styles. Chen Xiaowang and Chen Xiaoxing with yang style master Cui Zhongzan. Also features Wudang masters Priest Zhong Yun Long and Yuan. Available on DVD and HD download at http://emptymindfilms.com', 'Non-English', 690324, 'Entertainment', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/dwNXaQwjEr4/mqdefault.jpg', 'yan style, tai chi, trailer, movie'),
