(66, 'Yang Tai Chi 24 Form Back View', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F6rf5KdAKdE', 6, '480', 'International Tai Chi Champion Dr. Pauline Bao Performs Yang Tai Chi 24 Form Back View (Taiji 24 Form Posterior View) at Lakeside Park in Nelson, British Columbia (BC), Canada.\r\n\r\nThe Bao ACADEMY of Tai Chi & Kung Fu located in Nelson, BC, Canada offers Tai Chi and Kung Fu classes taught by Master Pauline Bao.', 'Non-English', 233884, 'Others', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/F6rf5KdAKdE/mqdefault.jpg', 'yan style, tai chi, 24 form'),
