(124, 'Part 4 Tai Chi: Learn it Here Free: Yang Cheng-fu ', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qrdoP3ax4Ng', 5, '240', 'To the untrained eye, Tai Chi Chuan seems too slow for combat. However, these soft movements conceal effective self-defense techniques', 'English', 74898, 'Tutorial,Entertainment,Application', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/qrdoP3ax4Ng/mqdefault.jpg', 'Tai Chi,Tutorial');
