(133, 'Tai chi for beginners - Chen style 2 Lesson 1', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sjzfA4dYMfg', 8, '720', 'Learn the basics of Tai chi for beginners from a real tai chi master. Master Wong tai chi available in Ipswich, Suffolk and online offers instruction with the best quality music and HD video. Yang style and Chen style form. Click here http://www.taichicombat.com/', 'English', 226344, 'Entertainment', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/sjzfA4dYMfg/mqdefault.jpg', 'yan style, demo, tai chi, beginer'),
(135, 'Master Heg Robinson - Telekinesis Demonstration | ', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sYW4yeBxMKA&feature=youtube_gdata', 5, '144', 'Telekinesis Master Heg Robinson (Boston, MAS.) \n\nHeg Robinson is my teacher''s teacher!', 'English', 56964, 'Tutorial', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/sYW4yeBxMKA/0.jpg', 'tai chi, demo, tutorial'),
(136, 'Tai Chi 24-form', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TBvF6r6DOvc', 4, '240', 'Tai Chi 24-form...\r\nIts a great martial art style. You should try it.', 'Non-English', 6001233, 'Tutorial', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/TBvF6r6DOvc/mqdefault.jpg', 'yan style, tutorial, demo, tai chi'),
(138, 'Tai Chi Application for Self-defense Fight in Chen', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tEbupVWZ6mk', 3, '480', 'Visit http://www.taichihealthways.com for more videos of Master Jesse Tsao on Yang, Chen, Wu, Sun tai chi tyle and Tai Chi sword, broadsword, qigong (Chi gong) meditation for internal energy healing, bio-energy, Shaolin and Wudang Taoist Kung-fu martial arts, Taiji Power Release (fajin), Taiji application, Bagua, Xingyi application. Tai Chi Health Ways host annual workshop with the top masters. See photos or videos of Chen Zhenglei, Li Deyin, Zhu Tiancai, Chen Xiaowang, Dan Lee, Su Zifang, Abraham Liu .... The martial aspect of Tai Chi is a hidden value of the ancient art. There are not enough references of Tai Chis applications in self-defense today because it has been de-martialized from its original fighting purpose to make its way into the general population. Master Tsao shares with you his research and 30 years of teaching experience in the major applications for Push Hands and self-defense in Chen Old Frame Routine One. Most of them are from Chen Zhenglei and Zhu Tiancais teachin', 'English', 737520, 'Group demo', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/tEbupVWZ6mk/mqdefault.jpg', 'yan style, group demo, tai chi'),
(139, 'Yang Taijiquan, 24 form', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tLxJsqV6qcM', 3, '144', 'This is full 24 form of Taijiquan Yang.', 'English', 558644, 'Entertainment', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/tLxJsqV6qcM/mqdefault.jpg', 'yan style, demo, tai chi, 24 forms'),
(140, 'Tai Chi Secret Movements, Applications & Peng, Lu,', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TsHek6oZYXU&feature=youtube_gdata', 2, '480', 'Check out his book How to Master Tai Chi Chuan''s Internal Secret at http://www.taichisecretmovements.com\n\nJoin him at Facebook Fan Page; http://www.facebook.com/#!/pages/Tai-Chi-Secret-Movements/147514718592749. \n\nTraining with Master Hiu who shares hidden methods on Internal Strength in his new book who sincerely hope that Tai Chi Chuan as precious gift from the Chinese to mankind can be spread far and wide to people all around the world.', 'English', 137508, 'Group demo', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/TsHek6oZYXU/0.jpg', 'tai chi, secret, demo'),
(141, 'Tai Chi Chuan - Chen Style Full Form', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U_yctN4uTQM&feature=youtube_gdata', 4, '720', 'Learn the moves from the movie tai chi zero! Master Wong offers training for beginners in Ipswich, Suffolk and online so you can learn to fight like a tai chi master! Click here http://www.taichicombat.com/', 'English', 53493, 'Application', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/U_yctN4uTQM/0.jpg', 'tai chi, demo, chen style, full form'),
(142, 'Yang Style Tai Chi Chuan - Great Grandmaster Hu Yu', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=us5Teds_n_Y', 4, '720', 'Yang Style Tai Chi Chuan performed by Hu Yuen Chou. Master Hu was a personal student of Yang Cheng Fu, one of the most famous Tai Chi teachers of all time.', 'Non-English', 62381, 'Entertainment,Application', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/us5Teds_n_Y/mqdefault.jpg', 'Sports, demo, chuan style'),
(144, '42 positions form tai ji quan', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V58I502J86M', 6, '240', 'This is the Tai Chi Yang style 2nd form, also known as the competition form, which has 42 positions drawn mainly from Yang style, but also from Wu and Chen.\r\nIt is very nice, but complicated to learn', 'Non-English', 72251, 'Entertainment', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/V58I502J86M/mqdefault.jpg', 'yan style, tai chi, 42 positions'),
(145, 'Tai CHi: Old Yang Style: Part 1: Learn for Free: M', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vgtsr_KomDs', 9, '240', 'http://www.taijiworld.com I will be slowly putting up the first third of the Old Yang Style free to learn from.\r\nThis video teaches the Old Yang Style of Yang Lu-Chan. This is the Yang style before it was changed by Yang Cheng-fu to what we know today. The movements are not all slow. There are fa-jing (explosive energy) movements all through this form. It is quite energetic with leaping kicks and explosive punches. This style was taught to Erle Montaigue by Chang Yiu-chun, one of the main students of Yang Shou-hou, the Brother of Yang Cheng-fu. Shou-hou did not change his grandfathers style. This video, because it is quite long does not include the basic qigong. It teaches both the martial art of Taijiquan\r\nand the healing art. www.taijiworld.com', 'English', 72191, 'Others', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/vgtsr_KomDs/mqdefault.jpg', 'yan style, tai chi, old style'),
(146, 'Tai Chi (Chen style) -- First Routine, Montreal', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vMAjEsWaZ1s', 10, '240', 'Chen style Tai Chi.\r\nVisit: internalstyle.com from Montreal, Canada', 'English', 65218, 'Tutorial,Entertainment,Application', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/vMAjEsWaZ1s/mqdefault.jpg', 'Tai Chi ,Tutorial, Demo, chen style'),
(147, 'Chen Man-Ching Short Tai Chi Form', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vsDPy7zMrA4', 9, '1080', 'This is a rare video of Chen Man-Ching performing the style of Tai Chi Chuan that we practice in our system. This is a short form of the Yang style Tai Chi Chuan. Im fifth generation down from Chen Man-Ching.', 'English', 365449, 'Tutorial', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/vsDPy7zMrA4/mqdefault.jpg', 'yan style, demo, short form'),
(149, 'Tai Chi self defense fight application Yang Style ', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W1ZkHc5xpmk', 2, '480', 'The martial application of Tai Chi. Internal Strength Qi Energy applied in self defense fighting. Fu Zhongwen student Xie Bingcan Yang style Tai Chi', 'Non-English', 80474, 'Group demo', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/W1ZkHc5xpmk/mqdefault.jpg', 'yan style, tai chi, demo, self defense'),
(151, 'Learn The Yang Cheng-fu Tai Chi Form Here Free', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6NdsyK8zPE', 5, '240', 'http://www.taijiworld.com I will be putting up the whole of the Yang Cheng-fu form step by step leaning free of charge over the next few days.\r\nThis video is the beginners video. It is the basic Yang Cheng-fu Taiji form taught in a step by step way so that one is able to literally teach oneself. This is the one that most people buy first of all regardless of how advanced they are. Every movement is gone over, stopping and starting to show important parts. Also included on this tape is the all important basic QIGONG, which is the most integral part of anyones Tai Chi training. This basic form is comprised of around 300 postures all linked together in an all flowing graceful whole, which when performed daily will aid in the healing of the body and mind. At an advanced stage, these movements are able to be used also for external self defence. This form is more healing than martial art, although it is said that Yang Cheng-fu changed the form only enough to leave in the internal essence of ', 'English', 362353, 'Tutorial,Others', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/w6NdsyK8zPE/mqdefault.jpg', 'yan style, tutorial, demo, tai chi'),
(152, 'Tai Chi Wrestling (taijiquan shuai jiao)', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WD0LH09D0Vo&feature=youtube_gdata', 1, '240', 'http://www.ymaa.com/publishing/dvd/taichi_DVD/taiji_wrestling_shuai_jiao \r\n\r\nTaijiquan Shuai Jiao Wrestling Takedowns from Push Hands', 'English', 63202, 'Entertainment,Others', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/WD0LH09D0Vo/0.jpg', 'Tai chi, information, Wrestling'),
(153, 'Tai Chi Übungen/Yang Stil Tai Chi 103er Form (Taij', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XEbEjzsc35s', 2, '480', 'Yang Tai Chi Hamburg. Yang Stil Tai Chi Chuan. Hier zur Übung die Grundfiguren des Tai Chi, Vogel am Schwanz packen.', 'English', 94826, 'Tutorial,Application', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/XEbEjzsc35s/mqdefault.jpg', 'Tai Chi,Tutorial, Demo'),
(154, 'Tai chi for beginners - Yang style Form Lesson 1', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xlHGjYHyjmM', 7, '720', 'Learn the basics of Tai chi for beginners from a real tai chi master. Master Wong tai chi available in Ipswich, Suffolk and online offers instruction with the best quality music and HD video. Yang style and Chen style form. Click here http://www.taichicombat.com/', 'English', 391054, 'Tutorial', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/xlHGjYHyjmM/mqdefault.jpg', 'yang style, demo, tutorial'),
(156, 'Yang Tai Chi for Beginners - Dr. Yang, Jwing-Ming ', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YonmpJvwmKM', 4, '720', 'See the DVD: http://ymaa.com/publishing/internal/t... \r\nLearn Tai Chi step by step with Yang, Jwing-Ming. Master Yang instructs the complete Tai Chi form from the front, and shows each movement one-by-one from multiple angles. There is also a rear view of the form that you can simply follow-along with once you''re familiar with the movements. \r\n\r\nDr. Yang''s tai chi lineage can be traced back to the Yang family through Grandmaster Kao, Tao (&#39640;&#28644;) and his teacher Yue, Huanzhi (&#27138;&#22864;&#20043;), an indoor disciple of Yang, Chengfu (&#26954;&#28548;&#29995;).', 'Non-English', 146257, 'Tutorial,Application,Group demo', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/YonmpJvwmKM/mqdefault.jpg', 'group, beginner, tutorial'),
(157, 'Become a Tai Chi Master in 5 Steps!', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yq3guYPRYzA&feature=youtube_gdata', 15, '720', 'Become a Tai Chi Master in 5 Steps!  These are my 5 Secrets to being the Ultimate practitioner of Tai Chi, Tai Ji Quan, and Qigong:\n\n#1:  Warm up Tai Chi Postures\n#2:  Practice of Solo Form\n#3:  Qi Gong Practice\n#4:  Stillness Meditation\n#5:  Tai Chi Fighting and/or Self Defense\n\nHit "SUBSCRIBE", Click "Like", Leave a Comment Below, Enjoy:\n\n***"LIKE" Our Facebook Page Here: https://www.facebook.com/JakeMace.TaiChi\n***"Follow"  Jake Mace on INSTAGRAM at "JakeMaceTaiChi"\n***"Follow"  Jake Mace on Twitter at "KungFuUniverse"\n\n***Order a DVD Below!  Thanks! :)\n\nORDER JAKE''S YANG TAI CHI DVD HERE, (Free Shipping in USA):\nhttp://www.shaolinarizona.com/Site_2/DVDs.html\n\nORDER JAKE''S IRON BONE DVD Here (Free Shipping in USA):\nhttp://www.shaolinarizona.com/Site_2/DVDs.html\n\nPlease subscribe to my channel and my vlog channel! I make new videos here everyday and make vlog''s about the Martial Arts way of life. \n-Jake Mace\n\nLook me up for a friend request on Facebook:  http://www.Facebook.com/JakeM', 'English', 131238, 'Tutorial', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/Yq3guYPRYzA/0.jpg', 'tai chi, defense, fight, secret'),
(159, 'Fu Zhongwen Yang-style Form Part 1', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zIpKW6AnKYw', 8, '240', 'Fu Zhongwen Yang-style Form Tai Chi.\r\n\r\nFu Zhongwen (1903-1994) was a respected Tai Chi Chuan teacher from China. From an early age, he had been a disciple of Yang Cheng-fu, and later a family member as he married Zou Kuei Cheng, the great-granddaughter of Yang Chien Hou.\r\n\r\nFu Zhongwen had dedicated his life to practicing and teaching Tai Chi. He was voted as one of the One Hundred Living Treasures of China and it was a great loss to the martial arts world and a greater loss to his family when he died in Shanghai on September 25, 1994 at age 92.', 'Non-English', 141141, 'Application', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/zIpKW6AnKYw/mqdefault.jpg', 'yang style, demo, tai chi'),
(160, 'Taiji: Chen Tai Chi Broadsword tai chi Dao', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zWhr9x5X7cM', 5, '480', 'Visit http://www.taichihealthways.com for more videos of Master Jesse Tsao on Yang, Chen, Wu, Sun tai chi tyle and Tai Chi sword, broadsword, qigong (Chi gong)for internal energy healing, bio-energy, Shaolin and Wudang Kung-fu martial arts.', 'English', 77378, 'Tutorial,Application', 'http://i.ytimg.com/vi/zWhr9x5X7cM/mqdefault.jpg', 'Tai Chi,Tutorial, Demo, Music, chen style');
